# Expo / React Native — Continuous Native Generation.
# ios/ and android/ are generated by `npx expo prebuild` from app.config.js and
# are NOT committed. Run `npm install && npx expo prebuild` (or `npm run prebuild`)
# before a native build; release builds use EAS or a prebuild step in CI.
